Keng [[botany]], ing '''berry''' iya ing karaniwan a uring balat [[bungang tanaman]], nung nu ing mabilug a [[ovary (plants)|ovary]] dingding lululut ya para apangan bilang [[pericarp]]. Deng bulaklak da reng tanaman a reni atin lang  [[ovary (plants)#superior ovary|superior ovary]] at atin lang metung o dakal pang [[carpel]] a atin maimpis a pabalat at malaman a kilub.  Deng butul makapakutkut la keng ovary. Deng alimbawang berries ilapin deng [[kamatis]], [[ubas]], [[litchi]], [[loquat]], [[plantain]], [[avocado]], [[persimmon]], [[balasenas]], [[bayabas]], [[uchuva]] (ground cherry), at [[chile pepper]].	


